      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "两个IngressController的命名能区分一下吗？虽然类型一样，但作用不同。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我可以用B和D来区分，B代表外部Ingress，D代表内部Ingress，这样图里能看出来是两个独立实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样就行。LoadBalancer是E对吧？它只连Etcd吗？",
