      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "不用，LoadBalancer只读Etcd就够了，流量转发逻辑由它自己决定。两个WorkerNode是C和G对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
